# Local debug scratch — never committed. ALL throwaway debug artifacts live here:
#   scratch/scripts/ — one-off investigation scripts (disasm probes, dumps, etc.)
#   scratch/out/     — their outputs (.txt/.out/.bin dumps, memory captures)
# New debug/research scripts and their outputs should be written here, not at the
# repo root or in tools/. Reusable diagnostic tools belong in tools/ (committed).
scratch/

